Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump is an insult to Kamala Harris. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: Jesse Watters: “Just weeks after CBS News moderators muted JD Vance's mic at the debate, the network was caught airing a deceptively dirty edit of Kamala Harris' interview on ‘60 Minutes.’ In the clip they promoted, she couldn't articulate her Middle East policy, but in the final cut her answer was coherent. The Trump campaign is demanding CBS release the raw interview.”
